Double First-Class (双一流) Data
---------------------------------
The Double First-Class (Shuang Yiliu / 双一流) round data included in
data/shuangyiliu_round1.json and data/shuangyiliu_round2.json is derived from
official announcements by the Ministry of Education of the People's Republic of
China. This is public government data.
